Since no species other than human is demonstrably capable of playing an MMRPG (though sometimes during actual gameplay I truly wonder):<br>
<br>
GM/DM->species = Human<br>
Player_in_PvP_conflict->species = Human<br>
Every_mob_you_fight_in_EQ->species = Computer<br>
<br>
Human = Human<br>
Human &lt;&gt; Computer<br>
<br>
