If you want MMORPG to be PvP based on P&P then you need a 6 to 1 or smaller player to GM ratio which is not profitable or have so many controls on it (soft caps) that someone will complain.   Overall though I do have to agree with many of the statement Scirocco made once you take into consideration balance of power in the game.  <p><a href=mailto:karl_saffell@hotmail.com>Kulothar</a></br>
