<br>
Moreover, you are leaping beyond my point.   Tudamorf (who probably has no hair left on his head at this point due to frustration) has accurately summed it up.   It's undeniable that a GM is HUMAN, I hope.  <br>
<br>
Whether the humans involved are &quot;equal&quot; (whatever that means), or good or bad at the game, is irrelevant.<br>
